  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Rinse your <strong>quinoa </strong>in a sieve under <strong>cold running water</strong>, then add it to a pot with a lid with 180ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[270ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[360ml]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 6-8 min or until all the water has absorbed and the quinoa is tender</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1580126069408-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1580126069408-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
